n.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_3275.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_3275.jpg 2000w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_3275-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_3275-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_3275-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_3275-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" /></figure><div class=\"wrap\"><i>総合職Ⅰ（法人営業）</i><h3>A.M</h3><span class=\"read-more\">Read more</span></div></a></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\"><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/interview/1893/\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_1994.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_1994.jpg 2000w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_1994-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_1994-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_1994-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AKO_1994-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" /></figure><div class=\"wrap\"><i>総合職Ⅰ（法人営業）</i><h3>B.K</h3><span class=\"read-more\">Read more</span></div></a></div></div></div><p class=\"link\"><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/interview/\" class=\"mod__button1\">Read more</a></p></section>\r\n\r\n\t<section id=\"active-field\">\r\n\r\n\t\t<div class=\"outer\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wrap\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t活躍フィールド\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>ACTIVE FIELD</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t仙台銘板ではさまざまな活躍フィールドを用意し、社員みんながそれぞれの「キャリアビジョン」へ向けてステップアップできる環境を用意しています。\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"./active-fields/\" class=\"mod__button2\">Read more</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</section>\r\n\r\n\t<section id=\"recruit\">\r\n\t\t<h2>採用について</h2>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"container\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"faq-bnr\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"./faq/\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"eager\" src=\"./assets/images/common/faq-banner01.jpg\" alt=\"Q&#038;A\" width=\"580\" height=\"400\"></figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wrap\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>よくある質問</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Read more</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</section>\r\n</main><!-- /main contents -->    <section class=\"mod__challenger\">\r\n    <i><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/assets/images/common/s-meiban-symbol.svg\" width=\"128\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"></i>\r\n    <h2>あなたの存在が、<br class=\"hideDT\">まだ見ぬ世界をつくりだす。</h2>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n      <p>\r\n        私たちは、革新力と突破力で安全・保安業界の道を切り拓いてきました。ここにあなたの力が加われば、当社はさらに高みを目指せるはず。それは、パワフルな行動力や斬新な創造力かもしれません。あなたの持ち前の素直さも、未来の当社にとっての大きな財産です。その力で、当社が築き上げたフィールドに新たな彩りを加えてください。何を描くか、何を生み出すかはあなた次第なのです。\r\n      </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"entry-buttons wow fadeInUp\">\r\n      <a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/career-info/#new_graduate\" class=\"entry\"><span>新卒採用</span><span>ENTRY</span></a>\r\n      <a href=\"https://s-meiban.snar.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"entry\"><span>キャリア採用</span><span>ENTRY</span></a>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </section><!-- footer -->\r\n<footer class=\"footer\">\r\n    <div class=\"footer__contact\">\r\n    <div class=\"footer__contact__container\">\r\n      <h2>CONTACT</h2>\r\n      <a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/contact/\" class=\"mod__button1\">お問い合わせフォーム</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n    <div class=\"footer__banner\">\r\n    <a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n      <h2>\r\n        <span>すべての現場に安全と信頼を</span>\r\n        <span>支える安全、<br class=\"hidePC\">支える未来。</span>\r\n        <span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/assets/images/common/logo.svg\" alt=\"株式会社仙台銘板\" width=\"248\" height=\"40\"></span>\r\n      </h2>\r\n      <p>コーポレートサイトへ</p>\r\n    </a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"footer__about\">\r\n    <div class=\"footer__about__container\">\r\n      <h2>\r\n        SENDAIMEIBAN\r\n        <span>RECRUIT</span>\r\n      </h2>\r\n      <div class=\"footer__about__container__link\">\r\n        <ul>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/about-us/\">私たちについて</a></li>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/works/\">仙台銘板の仕事</a></li>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/message/\">社長メッセージ</a></li>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/numbers/\">数字で見る仙台銘板</a></li>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/active-fields/\">活躍フィールド</a></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <ul>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/interview/\"><span>社員インタビュー</span></a></li>\r\n          <li>\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/career-info/\">採用について</a>\r\n            <ul>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/career-info/#flow\">採用情報・選考の流れ</a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/faq/\">よくある質問</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n          </li>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com/recruit/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.s-meiban.com\" target=\"_blank\">コーポレートサイト</a></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <small class=\"footer__about__copyright\">Copyright(C) Sendaimeiban All Rights Reserved.</small>\r\n    <div class=\"footer__about__pa